  "content_markdown": "Version: 8.1\nOn this page\nLevel: beginner\nnote\nCreatio AI is available for beta testing in Creatio version 8.1.5 Quantum to a closed test group. The general public release of the feature is planned in the near future.\nCreatio AI is an innovative tool powered by generative AI that transforms Creatio cloud and on-site experience into an intelligent and seamless workflow. It acts as Creatio AI, assisting in a variety of ways to enhance productivity and efficiency when you work with Freedom UI pages.\nFig. 1 Creatio AI\n![Fig. 1 Creatio AI](https://d3a7ykdi65m4cy.cloudfront.net/ac-en/s3fs-public/images/NoCode_Customization/copilot_overview/scr_copilot.png)\nCreatio AI redefines user interaction with Creatio Freedom UI, shifting the focus from how to what needs to be achieved. It empowers users to do the following:\n* **Perform System Actions** : Execute system actions within Creatio with ease, streamlining tasks and reducing manual effort.\n* **Get Data-Driven Answers** : Receive comprehensive and accurate answers to questions based on the rich data within the Creatio platform.\n* **Automate AI-Powered Tasks** : Automate repetitive tasks, such as generating descriptions, freeing up valuable time for more strategic endeavors.\n* **Elevate Productivity** : Focus on higher-level tasks and strategic thinking while Creatio AI handles the mundane, boosting overall productivity.\n* **Tackle Complex Challenges** : Leverage the power of generative AI and user-defined rules to tackle complex tasks with confidence.\nCreatio AI empowers users to achieve their goals without writing complex code. Its intuitive no-code interface enables users to describe desired outcomes using simple language, making it accessible to users of all technical backgrounds.\nCreatio AI does not work with graphics and widgets.\nTo access Creatio AI, click ![btn_copilot.png](https://d3a7ykdi65m4cy.cloudfront.net/ac-en/s3fs-public/images/NoCode_Customization/copilot_overview/btn_copilot.png) in the top right. You can interact with it using simple language. For example, ask it to translate text or provide an overview of a record page. Creatio AI also includes advanced customizable functions called intents. Use intents to enable users to perform a complex task as a single prompt without the need to do everything step by step. Learn more: [Develop Copilot intents](https://academy.creatio.com/documents?id=15631), [Intent development recommendations](https://academy.creatio.com/documents?id=15631).\nImportant\nThis functionality requires \"GenAIFeatures.Copilot\" and \"SidebarExtensions\" features to be turned on. Learn more: [Manage an existing additional feature](https://academy.creatio.com/documents?id=15631).\nCreatio AI is a paid feature that costs tokens per each request sent.\nYou can use Creatio AI in any language, but we recommend using English.\n* * *\n## See also\u200b\n[Develop Creatio AI intents](https://academy.creatio.com/documents?id=2535)\n[Intent development recommendations](https://academy.creatio.com/documents?id=2536)\n[Data privacy in Creatio AI](https://academy.creatio.com/documents?id=2529)",
